name: CutchSoft Private Limited
tag_list: cutchsoft, india, sme, small-and-medium-buisness, cheque-managment-software, cheque-printing-software
overview:
CUTCHSOFT is a prescient technology deliverer for small and medium companies.

CutchSoft was incepted in August 2009 to deliver simple, effective growth technologies to small and medium businesses to make them future-ready. In this short time, CutchSoft has gained the distinction of becoming one of the largest delivery partners for Tata Teleservices and is building knowledge-driven-relationship-networks to help SMEs adopt better technologies & business solutions.
